<br>
I have to say that this is a tactic I've suggested to many clerics in smaller guilds.  When they are clearly camping ragefire and they feel intimidated by larger guilds who pop in continuously this is the one thing that can/will save them.<br>
<br>
Even when you're only buying time to buff and prep your groups its the only sure way to keep yourself from being ganked by someone with more power who will win if they know that all they have to do is engage first.<br>
<br>
